Create a program that calculates the number of days, weeks, and months left if we live until 100 years old. 
The program should take your current age as input and output a message with the time left in this format:

  solution:-

  name = input("enter your name :-")
age = input("enter your age :-")
year = 92 - int(age)
weeks = 52 * year
months = 12 * year
days = 365 * year

print(f" hi {name} You have {days:,} days, {weeks:,} weeks, and {months:,} months left.")

  output:- hi veera You have 25,185 days, 3,588 weeks, and 828 months left .
